  "title": "Commodities MNC: Tax Manager (Open to candidates from Corporate Tax Advisory/Compliance)",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>*Seeking for a Tax Manager with minimum 5 years of Corporate tax, transfer pricing, current and deferred tax OR tax advisory/consulting experience* </strong></em></p><p><strong>THE COMPANY </strong></p><p>With their growth strategy in place, they seek to expand their reach in their Commodities Trading business. Currently, they seek for a Tax Manager to be part of their team. </p><p><strong>JOB RESPONSIBILITIES</strong></p><ul><li>Ensure tax compliance for Singapore and regional entities </li><li>Report and prepare tax returns and filings, current and deferred tax</li><li>Provide tax advisory on transfer pricing, intercompany, M&A or restructuring </li><li>Be involved in tax planning to help with cross-border transactions, FX exposures, optimize cash flow, improve Group’s effective tax rate</li><li>Liaise with auditors, and regulators to ensure compliance and good governance in a fast-paced trading environment</li><li>Any other adhoc duties</li></ul><p><strong>JOB REQUIREMENTS</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in Accountancy/Accounting/Commerce or ACCA or any other relevant education</li><li>Minimum 5 years of Corporate tax, transfer pricing and current and deferred tax OR tax advisory experience handling Commodities industries (From Tax advisory/consulting firms) </li><li>Meticulous, diligent, proactive, analytical and a team player </li></ul><p>If you will like to explore this opportunity, please email your resume in Microsoft\nWord format to marie@resolutehunter.com</p><p>We thank you for your interest and will contact shortlisted candidates for more detailed\ndiscussion.</p><p>For more job openings, please visit our website at https://resolutehunter.com/opportunities/ </p><p>EA Licence 18C9105  </p><p>EA Reg R1105305</p>",
